text: Sebastiaan Steur (born 8 March 1984, in Naarden) is a Dutch former footballer who played as a striker. He formerly played for FC Volendam, SC Heerenveen, SBV Excelsior, Heracles Almelo and Spakenburg. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:People from Volendam Category:Association football forwards Category:Dutch footballers Category:SBV Excelsior players Category:SC Heerenveen players Category:Heracles Almelo players Category:FC Volendam players Category:SV Spakenburg players Category:Eredivisie players
